All right. "Patricia,
tonight you will enjoy

13:04.650 --> 13:07.853
a romantic
one-on-one date with Philip."

13:07.953 --> 13:09.188
- Hey!
- Nice.

13:09.288 --> 13:10.456
Very nice.

13:10.523 --> 13:12.758
"Deneia."

13:12.825 --> 13:14.627
"Tonight you will enjoy

13:14.693 --> 13:18.130
a romantic
one-on-one date with Scott."

13:18.197 --> 13:20.199
All right.

13:20.299 --> 13:22.268
