- I know.

13:24.303 --> 13:25.638
"Kiki, tonight you will enjoy

13:25.704 --> 13:28.374
a romantic one-on-one date
with Grant."

13:28.474 --> 13:30.543
I made it. I made it!
Yes!

13:30.643 --> 13:33.112
All right, so you guys --
Say, you want to go get ready?

13:33.179 --> 13:34.880
- Yes. Let's do it.
- Let's do it.

13:34.980 --> 13:36.382
Let's do it.

13:38.484 --> 13:40.152
Come on, girls.

13:40.219 --> 13:42.054
Joel:
Bring it home for us.

13:42.154 --> 13:44.390
One thing's for sure --
I'm having me some fun,

13:44.490 --> 13:46.158
'cause I'm spending with -- If
I'm hanging out with Trish,

13:46.225 --> 13:48.060
I know I'm having fun.

13:48.160 --> 13:49.795
You know you are going
to laugh.

13:49.862 --> 13:51.363
Here. Do you want this
up or down?

13:51.463 --> 13:52.498
Whatever.

13:52.565 --> 13:54.133
Well,
just a little bit.

13:54.967 --> 13:58.070
You're looking fly
tonight, girl.

