So look at this, right?

14:11.417 --> 14:13.352
I know. It's beautiful.

14:13.419 --> 14:15.254
Ohh, man!

14:15.354 --> 14:17.590
Look at
all these beautiful...

14:17.690 --> 14:19.191
Joel:
Let's have a seat.

14:19.258 --> 14:21.427
...plants and everything.

14:22.895 --> 14:24.997
Plants.

14:25.064 --> 14:26.365
Oh, yeah.

14:26.432 --> 14:28.767
Right now, I would say
Stephanie is the one

